        <heading><span style="color:#0070C0"><b><u>Commentary on provisions of Act</u></b></span><marker name="tab" /><inline name="page"><b>3</b></inline></heading>
        <paragraph>
          <content>
            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Section 1 and Section 2: Meaning of ‘steel undertaking’ and Directions about use of assets</u></span><marker name="tab" /><inline name="page">3</inline></p>
          </content>
        </paragraph>
